snippet.textDisplay: Loved the song. Koi joh bhi kahe dil hai aur hamesha rahega Pakistani. Aur Chinese aur Japanese log aap ke dost waqai  hain lekin woh aap ka mulk theek nahin kar sakte na unhein karna chahiye. Jaise Hindustan ne Pakistan ko tabah karne ke liye koi kasar nahin chori isi tarah humein khud apne aap ko uthaana hoga aur Pakistan se hi apni pehchaan banani hogi warna hamara dushman humein khatam kar dega. Na hum Chini hain na Japani na hi Hindustani Hum sab Pakistani hain chahe kisi jagah se ya nasal se hon hum sab aik hi tasbeeh ke daane hain aur mil kar khud ko aage le ke jaayeinge toh hamare dost mumaalik bhi hamari kaamyabi mein hissa daaleinge. Pakistan Zindabad.
